        Width: 48.5   Length: 81   Height: 6
        Goal width: 8   Ball diameter: 2.5   Bar height: 4.8
        Formation: 1 (goalie) — 3 (defense) — 4 (midfield) — 3 (attack)
        Bar gap: 9.5   Bar-to-wall gap: 7.25 (adjusted to sum to 81)
        3-player spacing: 15   4-player spacing: 10.2
        Goalie bumper gap: 32

      Rod Y positions (from Yellow end -40.5 to Blue end +40.5):
        Y goalie  -33.25   Y defense  -23.75   B attack  -14.25
        Y midfield -4.75   B midfield   4.75   Y attack   14.25
        B defense  23.75   B goalie    33.25
